title: How has QOF achievement on asthma changed?
analysis_commentary: Performance against the asthma indicator group within the clinical domain can be used as an exemplar for other indicator groups in the QOF clinical domain; high achievement with limited variation over time and a dip in 2012/13.
data_source: Health & Social Care Information Centre, Quality and Outcomes Framework
